INSERT INTO public.tojung (id,num,total,jan,feb,mar,apr,may,jun,jul,aug,sep,oct,nov,"dec",created_at,nation) VALUES (361,'063','✨ 1. 2026 Overall Fortune
The year 2026 brings a period of confusion, like navigating through dense fog. It will be a year where finding direction proves difficult, as if lost in the mountains. With clouds obscuring the sun and an unclear path ahead, a realistic and calm approach is needed rather than high expectations. Greed or excessive challenges will only bring losses, requiring cautious behavior. Movement fortune is unfavorable, so it''s wise to stay in one place and wait for the right time. Situations of dilemma will frequently occur, leading to many sighs, but amid this there is a bright side—a good romantic connection will come your way, which you should cherish.

