Health-wise, pay attention to preventing winter colds, and stress management is important. Avoid overwork and get sufficient sleep. The western direction is relatively safe, with lucky colors being gray and white. Let go of impatience and spend the month calmly.','February is like living abroad, a month where finding direction in unfamiliar environments is difficult. However, with benefactors'' help, matters can be accomplished, so don''t lose hope. Cooperation and communication are important during this period.

